            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "As I know, there is no need for a trailing newline in the json spec.\r\n@justinmayhew If I'm wrong, can you please link the source that says that a newline is necessary.\r\n\r\nI would suggest to keep it as it is. Crappy tools that don't implement the spec properly, should loose. ",
